        <div class="bento-num">12</div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Best free tool: RankMath</h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">For WordPress sites that want <span class="accent">basic on-page optimization at zero cost.</span></h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">Free, real-time on-page scoring inside the WordPress editor. No SERP analysis or content generation — but hard to argue with the price.</p>
        <div class="bento-cta">See full review <span class="arrow">↓</span></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE TESTED -->
  <section class="problem-section">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">How we tested</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">12 tools, <span class="accent">6 weeks, real keywords.</span> Not feature comparisons.</h2>
      <p>We publish 30+ articles per month across 70+ industries and have used every tool on this list in production. The ranking is based on whether content actually moves in search — not on feature count, marketing claims, or vendor briefings. Pricing was verified in March 2026.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-grid">
      <div class="ba-col before">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">The core split</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Writing tools vs. optimization tools vs. full-pipeline tools.</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Most tools are one or the other. Very few are both.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Writing tools</h4>
              <p>Generate content faster. Jasper, Writesonic, Scalenut. Save production time. Don't guarantee rankings.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Optimization tools</h4>
              <p>Grade existing content against SERP data. Surfer, Clearscope, NeuronWriter. Improve performance. Don't generate content.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Full-pipeline tools</h4>
              <p>Handle research, writing, optimization, and publishing together. theStacc. Most people need this and don't know it exists yet.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>What we measured for each</h4>
              <p>SEO optimization depth, writing assistance quality, research integration, publishing pipeline, and pricing transparency.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-col after">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">What we found</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">The publishing gap is the biggest hidden cost in this category.</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">Four things became clear across 6 weeks of testing.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>20–40% ranking improvement from NLP optimization alone</h4>
              <p>When content structure is also correct, proper NLP optimization consistently beats keyword-stuffed content.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">02</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Publishing is the hidden time cost nobody lists on the pricing page</h4>
              <p>Formatting, images, CMS upload, meta fields — 30–90 minutes per article across every tool that stops at a draft.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Budget tools have closed the quality gap on low-competition keywords</h4>
              <p>Frase and NeuronWriter deliver 70–80% of Surfer's value at 20% of the price for informational content.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">04</span>
            <div>
              <h4>theStacc was the only tool that solved writing + optimization + publishing together</h4>
              <p>$99/mo, 30 articles fully published, zero editing or publishing labor. $3.30 per published piece.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">12<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Tools tested over 6 weeks</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$0<span class="accent"></span></div><div class="stat-label">Cheapest tool (RankMath — WP only)</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">$3<span class="accent">.30</span></div><div class="stat-label">Winner all-in cost per published article</div></div>
      <div class="stat-cell"><div class="stat-num">40<span class="accent">%</span></div><div class="stat-label">Avg ranking lift from NLP optimization</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RANKED LIST -->
  <section class="problem-section" id="ranked-list">
    <div class="problem-header">
      <span class="label-pill">The full ranked list</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">12 SEO content writing tools, <span class="accent">ranked by what moves rankings.</span></h2>
      <p>Each entry: rank, price, who it fits, verdict, three pros, one honest con. No filler.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- #1 theStacc -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-1">
      <div class="ba-col after" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#1 · WINNER · $99/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">theStacc — Best overall SEO content writing tool</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For anyone who needs content published, not just written or optimized.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">theStacc handles the entire content pipeline — keyword research, article generation, SEO optimization, image creation, and CMS publishing — without manual intervention. Connect your site, pick a brand voice, and 30 articles appear on your site each month. It also bundles Local SEO (30 GBP posts) and Social Media (30 posts) for an additional $49/mo each, with a 15% bundle discount. AI-search optimized — articles are structured to be cited in ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini, not just rank in Google.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Only tool on this list that writes, optimizes, and publishes without touching the keyboard</h4>
              <p>Every other tool requires manual steps at some point. theStacc is the only one where your involvement is: sign up, connect CMS, done.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>AI-search optimized — not just Google</h4>
              <p>40% of search traffic is now ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Claude. theStacc structures content to be cited by AI engines, not just to rank in traditional search.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✓</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Blog + GBP + Social in one platform</h4>
              <p>Most tools cover one channel. theStacc covers three — and bundles them with a 15% discount.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">✗</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Honest con: no technical SEO audits, backlink building, or manual NLP score customization</h4>
              <p>theStacc is a content production platform. For rank tracking, site audits, or link-building, you'll pair it with a separate tool like SE Ranking or Ahrefs.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/checkout/" class="btn btn-primary"><span>Start the $1 trial <span class="arrow">→</span></span></a>
          <a href="/modules/content-seo/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-left: 12px;">See Content SEO module</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #2 Surfer SEO -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-2" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#2 · FROM $89/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Surfer SEO — Best for NLP optimization scoring</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For content teams with writers who need the industry standard for SERP-based content scoring.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Surfer analyzes top-ranking pages for target keywords in real time, providing NLP-based content scores, keyword targets, heading structures, and word counts. The Content Editor shows exactly what to add or remove. Surfer AI generates pre-scored drafts at $29 per article. Google Docs and WordPress extensions are available. No auto-publishing — you still export, format, and publish manually.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Industry standard NLP scoring — the deepest SERP analysis in the category</h4><p>Surfer pioneered real-time NLP content scoring and still has the most granular analysis available. If you're optimizing competitive content manually, this is the benchmark.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Google Docs and WordPress extensions reduce workflow friction</h4><p>Score content without switching tools — works inside where your team already writes.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Content Planner generates topical clusters for authority building</h4><p>Identifies 20–50 related article opportunities to build topical authority systematically.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: $29/article for AI writing on top of $89/mo, and still no publishing</h4><p>30 articles costs $959/mo before editing and publishing labor. theStacc does 30 for $99, fully published.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #3 Clearscope -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-3" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#3 · FROM $170/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Clearscope — Best for enterprise content grading</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For large editorial teams that need an objective, letter-graded scoring system to standardize content quality at scale.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Clearscope grades content with letter scores (A++ through F) based on topic coverage against top-ranking pages. The grading system removes subjectivity from editorial feedback — everyone knows what an A article looks like. Google Docs and WordPress integrations are included. At $170/mo for 100 reports and $1,200/mo for Business, this is strictly an enterprise tool.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Letter grading removes subjectivity from editorial feedback</h4><p>A shared language across your editorial team. Everyone knows what "good enough" means without guessing.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Comprehensive NLP analysis from top 30 SERP results</h4><p>Wider competitor set than most tools — analyzes 30 ranking pages instead of 10 or 20.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Google Docs and WordPress integration</h4><p>Works inside existing writing environments without tool switching.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: optimization only — no writing, no publishing — at the highest price on this list</h4><p>$170/mo gets you content grades. You still need writers to create the content and someone to publish it.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #4 Frase -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-4" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#4 · FROM $15/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Frase — Best budget SEO content writing tool</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For solo creators who want real SERP research and NLP optimization without paying Surfer prices.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Frase combines SERP analysis, content brief generation, AI writing, and NLP scoring in one platform starting at $15/mo. The question research feature surfaces what people actually search around a topic — one of the most useful features in the category for low-budget content teams. AI writing quality is inconsistent but improving. No auto-publishing.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Most affordable SERP research and NLP tool on this list</h4><p>$15/mo for real competitor analysis, question extraction, and NLP scoring. The best entry-level option by a wide margin.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Question research identifies what searchers actually want to know</h4><p>Surfaces the questions driving search behavior around any topic — more useful than keyword volume data alone.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Writing and optimization in one interface</h4><p>No need to research in one tool and write in another.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: AI writing needs editing and Solo plan caps at 4 articles/mo</h4><p>The research is good. The AI writing is workable. The publishing and editing work falls on you.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #5 SEO.AI -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-5" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#5 · FROM $149/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">SEO.AI — Best premium SEO content writing tool</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For teams that need human QA on AI-generated content before it goes live.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">SEO.AI generates SEO-optimized articles and routes them through a human QA review before publishing. Schema markup is auto-generated. Publishing to 6+ CMS platforms is included. The human review layer catches factual errors and optimization gaps before anything goes live — useful for regulated industries or topics where inaccuracies are costly. Volume is limited by the review queue.</p>
        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Human QA catches factual errors before publication</h4><p>For healthcare, legal, financial, or technical content, this layer has real value. Accuracy matters more than speed.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Schema markup auto-generated with every article</h4><p>Article, FAQ, and structured data schema is created automatically — no manual schema coding.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Publishing to 6+ CMS platforms</h4><p>Closes the loop to your CMS without manual export and formatting.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: low volume (4–8 articles/mo) and 24–48 hour publishing delay</h4><p>The human QA is the feature and the bottleneck. If you need 30 articles/mo published fast, this isn't the tool.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #6 Scalenut -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="tool-6" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="ba-col before" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
        <div class="ba-head">
          <span class="ba-label">#6 · FROM $39/MO</span>
          <h3 class="ba-title">Scalenut — Best full-stack platform for speed</h3>
          <p class="ba-sub">For content teams that need a complete first draft in under 5 minutes with keyword planning and editorial management included.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Scalenut's Cruise Mode generates complete first drafts in under 5 minutes. Keyword planning, content calendar, and NLP optimization are bundled in one platform. Cluster identification helps build topical authority strategically. Quality is consistent on broad informational topics; technical and niche content is weaker. No real auto-publishing beyond a basic WordPress plugin.</p>
